"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-medium\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" src=\"https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2019/11/statistic-1820320_640-300x229.png\" alt=\"Grafiskt element som visar en sk√§rmbild med statistikuppgifter\" class=\"wp-image-1357\" srcset=\"https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2019/11/statistic-1820320_640-300x229.png 300w, https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2019/11/statistic-1820320_640.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption>Bild av anv√§ndaren <a href=\"https://pixabay.com/users/200degrees-2051452/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=1820320\">200 Degrees</a> p√• <a href=\"https://pixabay.com/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=1820320\">Pixabay</a></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nu har √•rets enk√§t till anv√§ndare och utvecklare √∂ppnats! Om du anv√§nder WordPress, eller om du arbetar med WordPress, ber vi att du ber√§ttar om dina intryck.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Det tar bara n√•gra minuter att fylla i <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-english\">enk√§ten (p√• engelska)</a> och resultatet ger oss goda insikter i hur WordPress anv√§nds. I √•r finns enk√§ten f√∂r f√∂rsta g√•ngen p√• 5 extra spr√•k:  <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-french\">franska</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-german\">tyska</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-japanese\">japanska</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-russian\">ryska</a> och <a href=\"https://wordpressdotorg.survey.fm/wordpress-2019-survey-spanish\">spanska</a>. Vi tackar de frivilliga i volont√§rn√§tverket som har hj√§lpt oss med √∂vers√§ttningarna!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enk√§ten kommer att vara √∂ppen i 4 veckor och resultatet kommer att publiceras i bloggen <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\">https://wordpress.org/news/</a> Alla uppgifter hanteras anonymt ‚Äì inga e-postadresser eller IP-adresser kommer att kopplas till n√•gra av de publicerade resultaten. Du kan l√§sa mer om hur WordPress.org hanterar personuppgifter m.m. i <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/about/privacy/\">integrititetspolicyn</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://sv.wordpress.org/2019/11/03/2019-ars-enkat-for-wordpress-anvandare-och-utvecklare/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:35:\"https://sv.wordpress.org/news/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:8:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Mon, 10 Oct 2022 13:40:55 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:6:\"x-olaf\";s:3:\"‚õÑ\";s:13:\"last-modifie